QuestData.Title: Hero's Call: Westfall!
QuestData.Description: By order of his royal highness, King Anduin Wrynn, all able-bodied citizens of the Alliance are to report to Lieutenant Horatio Laine at the Jansen Stead.$B$BWestfall has been overrun by beggars and transients, leading to a massive increase in criminal activity. Your help is needed to restore order to the populace. You can reach the Jansen Stead in Westfall by traveling west from Elwynn Forest.$B$BFor the glory and honor of the Alliance!
QuestData.LogDescription: Report to Lieutenant Horatio Laine at the Jansen Stead in Westfall.
